---
title: "US11 — Create / update fitness profile"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>FitnessProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateFitnessProfile
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>FitnessProfile
  A->>B: edit metrics, chips, tags - tap SAVE PROFILE
  B->>C: save(userId, patch)
  C->>E: updateFitnessProfile(userId, patch)
  alt saved
    E-->>C: updated FitnessProfile
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (refreshed)
    B-->>A: "Fitness profile saved."
  else write fails
    E-->>C: error
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not save. Please try again."
  end
  note over E: updateFitnessProfile via FitnessGateway → fitness_profiles (RLS: own row only).<br/>custom tags via addCustomTag → FitnessGateway.addCustomHealthTag
